### DDD Placement Rules

| What | Where |
|------|-------|
| Entity with business behaviour | `src/Domain/Model/` |
| Value object (e.g., Email, Money) | `src/Domain/ValueObject/` |
| Repository interface | `src/Domain/Repository/` |
| Doctrine repository implementation | `src/Infrastructure/Persistence/` |
{% if use_cqrs %}
| Command + Handler | `src/Application/Command/{FeatureName}/` |
| Query + Handler | `src/Application/Query/{FeatureName}/` |
{% else %}
| Application service (orchestrates domain) | `src/Application/Service/` |
{% endif %}
| Controller (HTTP wiring only) | `src/UI/Controller/` |

